# Reference local.properties for React Native 0.71.x
# This file should not be checked into version control

# Path to the Android SDK
# Use double backslashes on Windows
sdk.dir=C:\\Users\\username\\AppData\\Local\\Android\\Sdk

# Optional: NDK version if needed
# ndk.dir=C:\\Users\\username\\AppData\\Local\\Android\\Sdk\\ndk\\25.1.8937393

# Optional: If you want to use a specific NDK version
# ndkVersion=25.1.8937393

# Optional: If you need to specify the build tools version
# buildToolsVersion=33.0.0

# Optional: Java home if you need to specify a different JDK
# org.gradle.java.home=C:\\Program Files\\Java\\jdk-17
